        <div id="slide-5" class="main-slide hidden absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4 transition-all duration-500 z-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-6 md:p-12 w-full max-w-4xl border-t-8 border-katipunan-red relative h-full md:h-auto max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto custom-scroll relative z-20">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-katipunan-red mb-4 font-serif text-center">Pamprosesong Tanong</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-8 italic">Isulat ang mga sagot sa iyong kuwaderno o Activity Passport.</p>
                
